 and 
\begin_inset Formula $v_{y}$
\end_inset 

 along the 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset 

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset 

 axes, kept constant during every elementary stage (two real);
\layout Itemize

a logical variable which switches ON/OFF the tip-surface force;
\layout Itemize

a logical variable which switches ON/OFF the excitation signal applied to
